            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>Hello, I'm [Your Name]</h3>
                <p>
                    Write a compelling paragraph about yourself here. Talk about your journey 
                    into acting, what drives you, your approach to characters, and what makes 
                    you unique as a performer.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Add another paragraph about your personality, interests outside of acting, 
